# MusicPlayer.Queue.Entry

**Structure**

An entry for the playback queue of the music player.

## Declaration

```swift
struct Entry
```

## Initializers

- **init(_:startTime:endTime:)**: Creates an entry of the playback queue with a playable music item, and optional start and end times.

## Instance Properties

- **artwork**: The artwork of this entry of the playback queue.
- **endTime**: An optional end time for this entry of the playback queue.
- **id**: The unique identifier of this entry of the playback queue.
- **isTransient**: A Boolean value that indicates whether this entry of the playback queue has a transient music item.
- **item**: A music item that corresponds to this entry of the playback queue, such as a song or a music video.
- **startTime**: An optional start time for this entry of the playback queue.
- **subtitle**: The subtitle of this entry of the playback queue.
- **title**: The title of this entry of the playback queue.
- **transientItem**: A music item that corresponds to a recently inserted entry in the playback queue that has underlying items the music player still needs to resolve.

## Enumerations

- **MusicPlayer.Queue.Entry.Item**: An item that corresponds to an entry in the playback queue.

## Conforms To

- CustomStringConvertible
- Equatable
- Hashable
- Identifiable
